| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4635 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6b955ec9-28cf-5cc8-89b7-945ccdd0cd87"
